 a \mod b = r = \arctan(\tan(\frac{a\pi}{b}-\frac{\pi}2))\frac{b}\pi + \frac{b}2 
 r=\arctan(\tan(\frac{a\pi}{b}-\frac{\pi}2))\frac{b}\pi + \frac{b}2\\ =\arctan(\tan(m\pi + \frac{r\pi}{b}-\frac{\pi}2))\frac{b}\pi + \frac{b}2\\ =\arctan(\tan(\frac{r\pi}{b}-\frac{\pi}2))\frac{b}\pi + \frac{b}2\\ =(\frac{r\pi}{b}-\frac{\pi}2)\frac{b}\pi + \frac{b}2\\ =r-\frac{b}2 + \frac{b}2\\ 
